      <h1 class='title'>Boundary Commission for Scotland</h1>
    </div>
    <div class='commons-written-statements-sitting' id='content'>
      
      <cite class='section'>HC Deb 16 September 2004 vol 424 c1687WS</cite>
      <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_1687ws' title='Col. 1687WS &mdash; HC Deb 16 September 2004 vol 424 c1687WS' name='column_1687ws' href='#column_1687ws' rel='bookmark'>1687WS</a>
      <div class='hentry member_contribution'>
        <a name='S6CV0424P2_20040916_CWS2_218'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-peter-duncan' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0424P2_20040916_CWS2_218' title='Link to this speech by Mr Peter Duncan' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-peter-duncan" title="Mr Peter Duncan">Mr. Peter Duncan</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para">To ask the Secretary of State for Scotland whether he has received the final report of the Boundary Commission for Scotland. [187937]</p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution'>
        <a name='S6CV0424P2_20040916_CWS2_219'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-alistair-darling' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0424P2_20040916_CWS2_219' title='Link to this speech by Mr Alistair Darling' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-alistair-darling" title="Mr Alistair Darling">Mr. Darling</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para">I have not yet received the Fifth Periodical Report of the Boundary Commission for Scotland. As I indicated to the hon. Member on <a href="/written_answers/2004/sep/07/designated-accommodation#column_940w">7 September 2004,<span class="italic">Official Report,</span> column 940W</a>, while the Commission has until December 2006 to report to me, in the light of its progress so far it seems likely that the report will be received much sooner than this deadline. However, the timing is a matter for the Commission.</p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
